                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Et c’est une laveuse au lavoir",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+3",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Tapant ferme et dru sur la lessive.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si sa douceur n’est pas excessive,\nElle existe, mais il faut la voir,\nEt c’est une laveuse au lavoir\nTapant ferme et dru sur la lessive."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Il la veut blanche et qui sente bon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Et je crois qu’à force il l’aura telle.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Mais point ne s’agit de bagatelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3−6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Et la tâche n’est pas d’un capon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+3",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il la veut blanche et qui sente bon\nEt je crois qu’à force il l’aura telle.\nMais point ne s’agit de bagatelle\nEt la tâche n’est pas d’un capon."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et combien méritoire son cas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "De soigner ton linge et sa détresse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "f"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Humanité, crasses et cacas !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et combien méritoire son cas\nDe soigner ton linge et sa détresse,\nHumanité, crasses et cacas !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Sans jamais d’insolite paresse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "f"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "O douceur du plus fort des Ji.— K.a,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Tape ferme et dru, bonne bougresse !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "f"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sans jamais d’insolite paresse,\nO douceur du plus fort des Ji.— K.a,\nTape ferme et dru, bonne bougresse !"
        }
    ],
